 Two police officers are believed to have been killed following another attack on a police station in Anambra State.
The latest attack, which was said to have taken place at midnight on Wednesday, was on the Obosi Police Station.
However, police personnel drafted from other parts of the state are presently on ground.
This is the latest in a string of attacks on police officers and stations in the Southeast in recent weeks.
